  "time_ut": 1660788498,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dd6 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dd4. 8 \u0dc5\u0db8\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0d87\u0dc5\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Saw elephants bathing. 8 The village worker who picked up the child and threw it into the canal was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police say that an 8-year-old boy in Polgahawela was watching elephants being bathed, and when a village service officer came to the spot, he picked up the boy and threw him into the stream where the elephant was being bathed.",
        "The child's bones were broken and the Village Officer of Polgahawela Udopola Village Officer has been arrested in connection with the incident.",
        "Suspect Au. He is a 54-year-old man and will be produced in court today."
      ],
